um; color: #136ec2; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">齿龈内阿米巴</a>原虫，对口腔疾病如口腔溃疡、牙龈炎、牙周炎、牙齿出血、口臭、牙痛（火牙痛除外)，长期使用植雅牙膏，能大大改善或消除口腔疾病；另对蚊虫叮咬、脚气、痔疮，对于碰伤肿痛有很好的缓解作用。对咽喉炎、扁桃体炎、咽炎有良好的消炎症作用。妇女也可作为洁阴使用。对器具衣物上的油渍也有很不错的去污效果。</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>产品介绍</strong><strong>净化口腔，持久护理</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">植雅牙膏在第一军医大学（现<a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; color: #136ec2; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">南方医科大学</a>） 多年研究基础上，创出新配方。本品以现代工艺流程，提取出植物中的甙和酚，以高效成分有效促进口腔健康。</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong>净化口腔：</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">特含天然植物因子&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;植物甙+酚&rdquo;，有效促进口腔健康； 清洁牙齿污垢和口腔环境，控制微生物滋生环境，保持牙齿健康状态；持久固齿：植雅牙膏中的天然植物成分，对口腔溃疡、牙龈肿痛、牙周炎、牙龈出血、口臭、龋齿等均有预防和改善的作用。</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: #519cea; margin: 1px 0px 0px; width: 25px; display: block; float: left; height: 24px; color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 2px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 2px;\">2</span><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"2\"></a><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"sub576993_2\"></a><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; background-color: #ffffff; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 8px; display: block; float: left; padding-top: 0px;\">相关知识</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; float: right; margin-left: 10px; padding-top: 6px;\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; color: #3355aa; text-decoration: none;\" title=\"编辑本段\">编辑</a></span></h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 22px 0px 12px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; clear: both; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"2_1\"></a><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"sub576993_2_1\"></a>你知道吗？如何才能彻底清洁口腔？</h3>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">口腔内细菌多为厌氧菌，进食后口腔内残留的食物残渣能使细菌滋生，经发酵产生有害物质，影响口腔的健康，使用普通牙膏后能清除大部份细菌和食物残渣；</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">但由于口腔内有原虫类生物--齿龈内阿米巴原虫，其排泄物能给细菌提供养分，同时，原虫类生物还能消耗氧气，创造出厌氧环境，有利于厌氧菌的再次滋生。</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">植物甙+酚能清除及抑制口腔内阿米巴原虫，因而能有效减少细菌的再次滋生，彻底清洁口腔。</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 22px 0px 12px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; clear: both; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"2_2\"></a><a style=\"outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: medium; display: block; color: #136ec2; top: -50px; text-decoration: none;\" name=\"sub576993_2_2\"></a>小知识</h3>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 2em; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: normal; color: #333333; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">90年代初的一项普查发现：50%以上的人群其口腔内均有齿龈内阿米巴原虫； 口腔内原虫由于其危害性未受到足够重视，同时因其难以杀灭，故对口腔的卫生及健康造成很大的潜在危险。 使用方法：早晚各一次。</div>\r\n<p><img id=\"desc-module-2\" class=\"desc_anchor\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; display: block; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; height: 1px; color: #404040; clear: both; vertical-align: top; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border: 0px;\" src=\"http://a.tbcdn.cn/kissy/1.0.0/build/imglazyload/spaceball.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px;\">净化口腔，持久护理</span><br style=\"text-align: left; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word