Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">种以上的氨基酸（含必需八种氨基酸）、微量元素（钙、铁、钾、锌、硒、钠、镁、铜、锰、磷等）、维生素（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等）、蛋白质、白蛋白、黄酮、不饱和脂肪酸（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EPA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DHA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）等多种天然活性成份。</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">长期服用无任何毒副作用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">关于太岁</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:10.5pt;margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:10.5pt;margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;text-autospace:ideograph-other\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color:#222222\">神奇的生命体太岁肉灵芝历史记载</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color:#222222\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color:#222222\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;\"</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\">肉芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>在我国古代文献记载中被称为<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">太岁</span></span></a></span>\"</span>。古籍中将<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">肉芝</span></span></a></span>\"</span>与其它<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">灵芝</span></span></a></span></span>相提并论，标明它无毒，功能<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#091;</span>主治<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#093;</span>：使人<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>轻身不老，延年神仙<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>，定为<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>上品<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）《中华本草》书中称：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>《纲目》（注：指《本草纲目》）把历代有关灵芝类的记载加以引证，并提出了自己的见解。曰：芝类甚多&hellip;&hellip;其种属，不可不识。《抱朴子》（注：晋代葛洪著）云：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>芝有<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">石芝</span></span></a></span></span>、<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">木芝</span></span></a></span></span>、<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">草芝</span></span></a></span></span>、<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">肉芝</span></span></a></span></span>、<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">菌芝</span></span></a></span></span>，凡数百种也。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>说明我国古代记载的芝，种类比较复杂<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>（引自《中华本草》精装本上册<span lang=\"EN-US\">169</span>页<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>灵芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>项目）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 0cm;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\">《本草纲目》（<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#091;</span>明<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#093;</span>李时珍著）书中在石部第九卷<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>石芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>的项下，和菜部第二十八卷<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>的项下皆引《抱朴子》对<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>肉芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>形态描述为：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>肉芝状如肉，附于大石，头尾具有，乃生物也。赤者如珊瑚，白者如截肪，黑者如泽漆，青者如翠羽，黄者如紫金，皆光明洞彻如坚冰也。大者十余斤，小者三四斤。功能<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#091;</span>主治<span lang=\"EN-US\">&#093;</span>：捣末，或化水服，令人轻身，长生不老。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span>（引自《本草纲目》上册<span lang=\"EN-US\">577</span>页、下册<span lang=\"EN-US\">1708-1709</span>页）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\">明代医学家李时珍在《本草纲目》中确有记载。在《本草纲目》中李时珍把它叫做肉芝收入&ldquo;菜&rdquo;部&ldquo;芝&rdquo;类，与我们现在见到的灵芝<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>并称为&ldquo;本经上品&rdquo;。《本草纲目》里还列举了几部以&ldquo;芝&rdquo;为主的药方，说明对一些疑难病症有着特殊疗效，其共同的特点是：&ldquo;久食，轻身不老，延年神仙。而且由于它具有自生自长的特点<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>显得更加珍贵<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>所以历代帝王都千方百计去寻找它<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>其中据说古代帝王将相寻找<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">太岁肉灵芝</span></span></a></span></span>的故事，以秦始皇派遣徐福率领三千童男童女找药最为著名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体\">《史记&middot;秦本纪》载：秦始皇统一六国后，听说东方有一种仙药，食用以后可以长生不老、得道成仙，于是在秦二十八年（公元前<span lang=\"EN-US\">219</span>年）<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>秦始皇命徐福率&ldquo;童男童女三千人&rdquo;和&ldquo;百工&rdquo;，携带&ldquo;五谷子种&rdquo;，乘坐八十五艘大船东渡，寻找长生不老的仙药其中一味&mdash;&mdash;就是<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">太岁</span></span></a></span></span>&ldquo;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.taisui.net.cn/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">肉灵芝</span></span></a></span></span>&rdquo;。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">【主要功能】</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（吡咯喹啉醌）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">世界医学界称之为第十四种维生素。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">现已研究证实，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">太岁肉灵芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">菌中含吡咯喹啉醌（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">pyrroloquinoline quinone )</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的特殊有效成份，日本学者于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2003</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年证实</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为新型水溶性维生素，其研究成果发表于国际权威杂志《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nature</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》上。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">准确的说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是一种氧化还原酶辅基，它非常稀少的存在于一些微生物、植物和动物组织中，不仅参与催化生物体内氧化还原反应，而且还具有一些特殊的生物活性和生理功能。微量的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">就能提高生物体组织代谢和生长机能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对人体十分有益的八大功能：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、作为人类发育的必要因子，刺激人体细胞生长如人体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">细胞、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">细胞，使之产生抗体，从而全面提高人体免疫功能；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、能显著降低血清胆红素，谷丙转氨酶水平，保持肝功能正常，并能有效防治肝损伤；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、双向调节自由基，能防治自由基过多造成的机体损害并引发各种疾病，如心脏病、癌症以及各类炎症；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、能促进神经因子合成，治疗各种神经系统疾病；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、能防治老年痴呆症和改善人体记忆；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是醌蛋白酶的辅基，参与呼吸链电子传递，在人体内通过葡萄糖的作用促进了氨基酸的吸收；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、刺激生物生长，能刺激人体细胞生长，增加细胞密度；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、能促进机体谷胱甘肽合成，防止白内障发生和肝脏胆红素积累。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">目前在国际市场上提纯后的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">售价为每克</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">39000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">美元，是黄金价格的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">多倍！</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">二）核酸</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">提高免疫力；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗氧化作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">影响脂肪代谢；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">促进细胞再生与修复；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗放射线和化疗损伤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">改善痴呆等神经障碍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">维持肠道正常菌群</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">影响营养素利用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">其他作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">饮食核酸可提高机体对环境变化的耐受力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">具有显著的抗疲劳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">增强机体对寒、暑的抵抗力、促进氧气利用、促进生殖系统的发育等作用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">三）几丁质</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">世界卫生组织将其称为强力免疫性食品。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">预防感染，防止病原体对人体侵害；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">免疫监视，监视自身癌细胞；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">细胞更新，维持各器官生理平衡，防止自身免疫性疾病；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">能被人体所吸收，和人体细胞组织有很好的亲和性；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抑制癌细胞转移，和血管壁细胞膜上表面接着分子附着的特性，使癌细胞不能随着、移动，封锁癌细胞转移途径。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以诱导免疫细胞的分化，修复受伤细胞</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以使血清渗透力增强，血清蛋白吸着了增强；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">四）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BRM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（生物体激活物质）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可调动激活人体的免疫系统，并提高免疫功能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">五）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（皂甙）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">又称皂素，其药理作用：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">双向调节免疫作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗缺氧和抗疲劳作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗低温应激作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗脂质氧化作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对中枢神经系统的作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抗致突变作用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抑制癌细胞成长</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">六）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（多糖类）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">构成生命的四大基本物质之一，在抗肿瘤、抗炎、抗病毒、降血糖、抗衰老、抗凝血、免疫促进等方面发挥着生物活性作用。具有免疫活性的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">太岁肉灵芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有抗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HIV</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">活性、抗凝血活性、抗肿瘤活性等多种活性成份。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">七）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">种以上的氨基酸</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">生物功能大分子蛋白质的基本组成单位，构成动物营养所需蛋白质的基本物质。包括人体必需八种氨基酸（人体内无法自身合成）：赖氨酸、色氨酸、苯丙氨酸、蛋氨酸、苏氨酸、异亮氨酸、亮氨酸、缬氨酸；以及非必需氨基酸（机体自身能合成，但自身合成量无法达到人体需要）组氨酸、精氨酸、天门冬氨酸、丝氨酸、谷氨酸、甘氨酸、丙氨酸、酪氨酸、氨、脯氨酸、胱氨酸、羟脯氨酸、门冬酰胺、半胱氨酸。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）含人体必需八种氨基酸（人体内无法自身合成）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）非必需氨基酸（机体自身能合成，但自身合成量无法达到人体需要）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">八）微量元素（钙、铁、钾、锌、硒、钠、镁、铜、锰、磷等）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">微量元素通过与蛋白质和其他有机基团结合，形成了酶、激素、维生素等生物大分子，发挥着重要的生理生化功能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">每种微量元素都有其特殊的生理功能，管它们在人体内含量极小，但它们对维持人体中的一些决定性的新陈代谢却是十分必要的。一旦缺少了这些必需的微量元素，人体就会出现疾病，甚至危及生命。如缺锌可引起口、眼、肛门或外阴部发红、丘疹、温疹。又如铁是构成血红蛋白的主要成分之一，缺铁可引起缺铁性贫血。机体内含铁、铜、锌总量减少，均可减弱免疫机制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">抵抗疾病力量</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，降低抗病能力，助长细菌感染，而且感染后的死亡率亦较高。微量元素在抗病、防癌、延年益寿等方面都还起着不可忽视的作用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">九）维生素（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">维持人体生命活动必需的一类有机物质，也是保持人体健康的重要活性物质。维生素在体内的含量很少，但在人体生长、代谢、发育过程中却发挥着重要的作用。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人体有如一座极为复杂的化工厂，不断地进行着各种生化反应。其反应与酶的催化作用有密切关系。酶要产生活性，必须有辅酶参加。已知许多维生素是酶的辅酶或者是辅酶的组成分子。因此，维生素是维持和调节机体正常代谢的重要物质。可以认为，维生素是以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">生物活性物质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的形式，存在于人体组织中。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十）蛋白质</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">蛋白质是一切生命的物质基础，是肌体细胞的重要组成部分，是人体组织更新和修补的主要原料。人体的每个组织：毛发、皮肤、肌肉、骨骼、内脏、大脑、血液、神经、内分泌等都是由蛋白质组成，所以说饮食造就人本身。蛋白质的功能是构成机体细胞和组织，促进生长发育，参加机体物质代谢，形成抗体，增强免疫能力和供给热能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">提供多种氨基酸，帮助身体建造新组织和修补更新；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在体内制造各种酶，有助于将食物转化为能量；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">维持体内水分及酸碱平衡；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过血液中的血红蛋白向细胞输送氧和各种营养；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">免疫作用；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">催化作用，使新陈代谢迅速进行；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">通过激素调节生理机能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十一）白蛋白</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人体血浆中的一种功能大分子蛋白质，是提供平衡氨基酸，维持血浆渗透力，增加血容量等重要成份。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">调节免疫功能；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">提高人血清蛋的含量，改善微循环。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">调整肠道菌群，促进消化系统食物的转化，促进铁的吸收。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十二）黄酮</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对人体的健康具有广泛的作用，如抗炎症、抗过敏、抑制细菌、抑制病毒、防治肝病、防止血栓形成、防治心脑血管病、抗肿瘤等。</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">人体自身不能合成类黄酮，黄酮类化合物由于代谢快，在体内不蓄积，需要经常补充。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十三）不饱和脂肪酸（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EPA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DHA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">EPA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">具有帮助降低胆固醇和甘油三酯的含量，促进体内饱和脂肪酸代谢。从而起到降低血液粘稠度，增进血液循环，提高组织供氧而消除疲劳。防止脂肪在血管壁的沉积，预防动脉粥样硬化的形成和发展、预防脑血栓、脑溢血、高血压等心血管疾病。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">DHA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是大脑营养必不可少的高度不饱和脂肪酸，它除了能阻止胆固醇在血管壁上的沉积、预防或减轻动脉粥样硬化和冠心病的发生外，更重要的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DHA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对大脑细胞有着极其重要的作用。它占了人脑脂肪的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">％，对脑神经传导和突触的生长发育极为有利。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">-------------------------------------------------------------</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoTitle\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria\">破解千年之迷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">----</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;mso-hansi-font-family:Cambria\">肉灵芝</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:15.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5; line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中国人一般都知道&ldquo;谁敢在太岁头上动土&rdquo;这句话，但却很少有人知道&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;是何物。&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;到底是什么东西？古书云：&ldquo;太岁如君，为众神之首，众煞之主，有如君临天下，不可冒犯&rdquo;。由于&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;位高权重，古人对他都非常敬畏，惟恐触怒了它而于己不利。为避免得罪&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;神，在冲犯&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;之年必须在新年开春期间拜祭它，以祈求新的一年平安顺利、逢凶化吉。据史料记载，&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;是古人假定的一个天体，和岁星</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">木星</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">运动速度相同而方向相反。&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;到了哪个区域，就在相应的方位地下有一块肉状的东西，这就是&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;的化身，在这个方位动土就会惊动&ldquo;太岁&rdquo;。这就是&ldquo;谁敢在太岁头上动土&rdquo;的由来。据专家介绍，<span style=\"color:#333333\">太岁是一种多菌种复合体，它不是动物、不是植物、也不是菌类，但是具备动物、植物和菌类的共同特点，有呼吸、有排泄、有的还有细胞结构、像动物但没头没脚。能自己进行微量的光合作用，还可以释放活性物质，像植物，但没根没叶。把野生太岁晒干了再放在水里还能恢复原样。</span>也叫肉灵芝。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:15.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5; line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在中国几千年前的古籍《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/11017.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">山海经</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》中就有关于太岁的记载。在《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/11017.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">山海经</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》中太岁也被称为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">视肉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">聚肉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">肉芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。你看都带个肉字，说明可以食用。据《山海经》记载，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">视肉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">最早是作为古代帝王生前喜欢食用的物品出现在古帝陵前的。具有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">食之尽，寻复更生如故</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">食一片复一片</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的特点，也就是说吃一片，它自己可以再次生长。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:15.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5; line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">太岁是长生不老的仙药明代医学家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/5910.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">李时珍</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/6320.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">本草纲目</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》中确有记载。据《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/6320.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">本草纲目</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》记载</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">肉芝状如肉。附于大石，头尾具有，乃生物也。赤者如珊瑚，白者如截肪，黑者如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/31766.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">泽漆</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，青者如翠羽，黄者如紫金，皆光明洞彻如坚冰也。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/6320.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">本草纲目</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》中李时珍把它叫做肉芝收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">菜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类，与我们见到的灵芝并称为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">本经上品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。《本草纲目》里还列举了几部以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为主的药方，说明对一些疑难病症有着特殊疗效，其共同的特点是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">久食，轻身不老，延年神仙。而且由于它具有自生自长的特点，显得更加珍贵。所以历代帝王都千方百计去寻找它，其中据说古代帝王将相寻找肉灵芝的故事，以秦始皇派遣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.cn/view/41778.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\" lang=\"EN-US\">徐福</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">率领几千名童男童女找药最为著名。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">西北大学生物研究室主任对太岁进行研究测试，结果表明：&ldquo;太岁肉灵芝&rdquo;富含核酸、多糖、几丁质和酵母菌、白地霉、硒、锗等数十种珍稀营养物质，能增加人体三种力：免疫力、自愈力和代偿力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">国外称肉灵芝为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">免疫之王</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，它被生物学家认为是和大熊猫一样都是大自然遗漏的古生物活化石，它产生的年代可以上溯到地质年代的白垩纪，是地球上发现的最古老的古生物活体标本，正如美国科学家研究证实的结果一样，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">它是人类和一切动植物的祖先</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:15.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5; line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现代医学认为，每个人身体中都有肿瘤恶变的细胞，长期服用肉灵芝液能延年益寿，增强自身免疫力，对高血压，胃溃疡，冠心病，美容键体等多方面都有很好的疗效。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，肉灵芝对延缓衰老，消除疲劳、高血压、动脉硬化、高血脂、冠心病脑中风、心肌梗塞、糖尿病、脂肪肝、骨质疏松、痴呆症、癌症、风湿病等有明显的防治作用，还能强化肝脏机能，调节神经内分泌系统，调节免疫功能，清除体内自由基等等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\" lang=\"EN-US\">3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，研究证实，&ldquo;太岁肉灵芝&rdquo;菌中含有一种名叫吡咯喹啉醌的特殊有效成份，简称<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>&ldquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span>&rdquo;它是一种氧化还原酶辅基，科学家们进行了大量的研究，尤其是深入地探讨了其特殊的生理功能，总结出<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;PQQ</span>对人体十分有益的八大功能：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">①、作为人类发育的必要因子，全面提高人体免疫功能；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">②、保持肝功能正常，能显著降低血清胆红素<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>谷丙转氨酶水平<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>有效防治肝损伤；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">③、防治自由基过多造成的机体损害并引发各种疾病，如心脏病、癌症以及各类炎症；<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">④、促进神经因子合成，治疗各种神经系统疾病；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑤、防治老年痴呆症和改善人体记忆；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑥、<span lang=\"EN-US\">PQQ</span>在人体内通过葡萄糖的作用促进氨基酸的吸收；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑦、刺激人体细胞生长，增加细胞密度；<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">⑧、防止白内障发生和肝脏胆红素积累。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.75pt;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">作为肉灵芝唯一<span style=\"color:red\">继承人酿药大师熊新元先生</span>，综合患者服用太岁第一、二代产品后反馈的情况，经心研制的第三代&ldquo;太岁甘露霖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">口服液&rdquo;，<span style=\"color:red\">以道家传承的太岁母液为培养基，</span>通过国家肉灵芝发明专利号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">201210370982.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，有效成分等肉灵芝复合粘菌体是纯天然的生物，不添加任何化学成分，就像我们所了解的冬虫夏草、人参、灵芝这些自然生物一样，但其价值远远超过他们市场药用价值的几十倍甚至几百倍。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:15.75pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5; line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;太岁甘露霖口服液&rdquo;<span style=\"color:red\">加入冬虫夏草、人参、黄芪、枸杞、首乌、甘草等</span></span><span style=\"color:red\" lang=\"EN-US\">81</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red\">味纯天然药材，经二十','2646','保健品	保健品牌	太岁','太岁','0','','','1','0',null,'1401652536','1403032190','92','data/files/store_275/goods_112/small_201406021155122251.jpg','1','2595','2644','2646','0','100.00','500','');
