ing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #990000; font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #666666;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">新华网 电脑辐射危害身体 可致十九种疾病</span></span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #990000; font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #666666;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #666666;\"><span><span style=\"color: #3366cc;\"><strong>http://www.cq.xinhuanet.com/news/2006-05/29/content_7119039.htm</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #ff66cc; font-size: large;\"><strong>产品名称： 富迪健康科技陶瓷刮痧片（防辐射型）</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #ff66cc; font-size: large;\"><strong>本款设计特别，可当饰物佩带，送礼送健康，首选哦</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #ff66cc; font-size: large;\"><strong>孝敬父母或领导，关爱身边的人，特别是孕妇和经常使用电脑的年轻人。</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">刮痧片设计时考虑到人们佩带于胸前，而且是按项链、吊坠的形式而设计。它能将辐射到刮痧片上及其周围的各种有害电磁波&ldquo;牵引&rdquo;到刮痧片中，将电磁波能量转换成热能。所以刮痧片即能刮痧，又能作为饰品，还具有预防电磁辐射危害、保护人体健康的作用</span>。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #336600;\">富迪健康科技有限公司生产的这款陶瓷刮痧片由&ldquo;吸波材料&rdquo;及稀有元素&ldquo;钛&rdquo;和&ldquo;锗&rdquo;制成。不仅有很强的防辐射功效，并能通过其中含有的稀有元素来改善人体自愈系统,使每个人都能做自己的保健师。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\"><strong>背景分析</strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp; 当今社会，电器设备如电视、电脑、计算机、手机、微波炉等的广泛应用，给人们的生活带来了极大的便利，但同时也带来了一个不可忽视的问题：电磁辐射问题。电磁辐射是一种物理现象，是指能量以电磁波的形式由源发射到空间的现象。电磁辐射对人体健康带来的不良影响已经引起众多专家的密切关注。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><br /><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 相关研究表明，电磁辐射对人体有六大害处：影响人类的生殖系统、影响人们的心血管系统、影响人们的视觉系统、可导致儿童智力残缺、诱发癌症并加速人体癌细胞增值、增加儿童患白血病的机率。科技日报曾报道，我国每年出生的2000万儿童中，有35万为缺陷儿，其中25万为智力缺陷，有关专家提醒育龄妇女，电磁波污染的危害最大；英国泰晤士报也曾报道，匈牙利科学家发现，经常携带和使用手机的男性的精子数目可减少多达30%，英国的实验报告指出，老鼠被手机微波辐射5分钟，就会产生DNA病变，人类的精、卵子长时间受手机微波辐射，也有可能产生DNA病变。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><br /><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 由于现代科学技术发展的需要，我们欲彻底消灭电磁辐射的污染已是不可能的。当前，富迪健康科技有限公司推出的防辐射陶瓷刮痧片，为人类的健康做出积极的贡献。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/205204216/T2fLOBXbpXXXXXXXXX_!!205204216.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">本品设有男式和女式两款购买时请留意</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">男款：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/205204216/T21fKBXbRXXXXXXXXX_!!205204216.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\">刮痧片的材料</span></strong><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防辐射陶瓷刮痧片是以吸波材料为主且由多种稀有元素经高科技特殊工艺（高温、恒压）化合而成，在10MHz～3GHz频率范围内有很强的吸波性能，其吸波频带宽包括了手机、电脑、电视等所有家电产品产生的电磁辐射。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><br /><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #008000;\">&nbsp;稀有元素&mdash;&mdash;钛，是一种亲生物金属。它可以调节电流，松弛精神，提高人体运动机能，还可通过调节局部热量，使肌肉放松，刺激血液流动帮助清除血液中由疼痛产生的作用物和疲劳因子。此外，它对缓解粘液囊炎，坐骨神经痛、头痛、关节炎及经前综合症等有明显作用。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><br /><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;稀有元素&mdash;&mdash;锗，锗石的远红外线是人体最适合的吸收频率和波长，可吸附分解人体内有毒物质和重金属，达到排毒养颜的作用。其凉血止血、降逆止呕、清火平肝的功效，历来受到人们青睐。此外，它还具有调整人体不正常电位，抑制癌细胞电位上升，促进血液循环，减轻疲劳，预防癌症，防止老化等作用</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><br /><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\"><strong>刮痧片的防辐射原理</strong></span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">刮痧片中的复合型吸波材料对电磁波都很敏感，特别容易使射入的电磁波微观粒子产生旋转、位移，这种转动和移动会大量消耗电磁波能量，从而实现对电磁辐射的吸收。（详见国际权威检测机构：摩尔实验室的刮痧饰品系列产品的检测报告）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><br /><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\"><strong>刮痧片的功能</strong></span><br />&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1、防辐射功能：刮痧片能将辐射到刮痧片及周围的各种有害电磁波吸收到刮痧片中，将电磁波能量转换成热能耗散，达到预防电磁辐射危害、保护人体健康的作用。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><br /><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2、刮痧功能：采用高精密生物功能材料压制而成，掌握阴升阳降的原理，在不适部位刮动，或按经络对应部位刮痧，有效缓解不适情况，配与富迪激能活络刮痧精油使用，兼着护肤功效，效果更佳。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.5pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #f6b26b;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-siz