transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 【性 状 】本品为棕褐色至黑褐色的膏块；味甘、微苦</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 【功能主治】补气养血，调经散寒。行经腹痛，子宫壁薄，女士补雌。孕前养子宫，</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 产后养气血，产后调理，是孕前产后的传统佳品。用于调理痛经、月经不调、多囊卵巢综合症、宫寒不孕、气血两亏、手脚冰凉、虚弱消瘦、子宫内膜薄、习惯性流产、性冷谈及寒湿所导致的白带量多，延更年期、美容养颜等，被古人称为女性滋补的圣品。</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 【用法用量】 口服，一次10克，一日2次，温黄酒或温开水服下。</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 【贮 藏】冰箱冷藏保存。</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> 【 注意事项 】</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> １、忌食寒凉生冷、辛腥辣食物。</span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 16px/25px Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #000000; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-widt