<br />该酒富含生命所必需的各种营养物物质；其色似宝石瑰丽，其状如九天甘露，唇初沾而馨绵，口将咽而生甜，温胃暖腰，回味无穷。长期饮用、延年益寿！<br />特点：<br />一、太岁典藏 &mdash;&mdash;&nbsp; 一种免疫增强剂<br />二、太岁典藏&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一种有效的抗衰老剂<br />三、太岁典藏&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一种性肾功能提升剂&nbsp;<br />健康&ldquo;白酒&rdquo;&not;&mdash;太岁典藏<br />中国人自古好饮酒，经过千百年的流转，那泓琼浆玉液已经渗透到华夏文明的各个领域。无数名门大家，在杯盏之间不断领略和传授以酒养生、以酒悟道的法则。<br />太岁典藏千年传承，以中医理论为依据，以天然药食草本为原料，古老&ldquo;工艺&rdquo;与现代生物技术相融合，经过24道工序精心制备而成。<br />她是一种新型多糖类的高级健康饮品，集白酒、红酒、药酒之综合优势，<br />从功能、口感、色泽等方面，满足人们追求时尚、优雅、健康之需求。<br />酌量品饮，补充体能，消除疲劳，补肾抗衰。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; widows: 2; line-height: 20px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; orphans: 2; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; widows: 2; line-height: 20px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; orphans: 2; color: #333333;\"><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_71/201406011634312557.png\" alt=\"2.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_73/201406011634333621.png\" alt=\"3.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_75/201406011634358418.png\" alt=\"4.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_18/201406011756587089.png\" alt=\"5.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_19/201406011757008562.png\" alt=\"6.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_21/201406011757013077.png\" alt=\"7.png\" /><img src=\"http://www.linglegou.com/data/files/store_275/goods_22/201406011757024129.png\" alt=\"8.png\" /></p>','2646','保健品	保健品牌	太岁','太岁','0','','','1','0',null,'1402264095','1403211103','156','data/files/store_275/goods_141/small_201406091349015486.jpg','1','2595','2644','2646','0','780.00','0','');
