=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://img1.tcgimg.com/Uploadfiles/bbs/2013/8/22/635127719308936564.jpg?f=1306449\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"800\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://img1.tcgimg.com/Uploadfiles/bbs/2013/8/22/635127720661314934.jpg?f=1306453\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"800\" /><br /></span></p>\r\n</p>','1233','护肤彩妆	精华','沛缇','0','','','1','0',null,'1402450982','1402450982','219','data/files/store_79/goods_79/small_201406111741197578.jpg','1','1227','1233','0','0','598.00','200',',沛缇优酵365饮液,益生源饮液,排宿便清肠胃,');
