\">、初次使用前，应将内胆洗涤干净。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、先用少量热水或者冰水洗涤内胆，（切勿使用钢丝球清洗）然后倒掉</span>,<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">再重新灌装开水或者冰水，以确保保温效果更佳</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 宋体; color: #cc0000;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000;\">3<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、每次使用后，请清洗干净，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\">保持干燥。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\">4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、不宜长久储存炭酸饮料于杯内，以延长保温杯的使用寿命。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\">5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、切勿靠近热源，不宜猛烈撞击。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; color: #cc0000; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\">6<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、置于小孩接触不到之处，以免烫伤。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11.75pt; margin-top: 11.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体 sans-serif\'; font-weight: bold; color: #cc0000; mso-spacerun: \'yes\';\">注意事项：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11.75pt; margin-top: 11.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1