line-height: 21px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; color: #404040;\">\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0033;\">瑞倪维儿</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0033;\">蛋白魔纤冲调粉，每天2袋，让身体水桶没短板</span>！</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 先看看，每百克瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉都含有哪些营养素：</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">蛋白质：41.33g</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">脂肪：3.86g</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">碳水化合物：19.35g</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">膳食纤维：13g</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">矿物质及微量元素：钾 4375mg、钠 4000mg、钙1750mg、磷1450mg、镁775mg、硒85m、锌24.25mg、锰6.5mg</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">维生素：V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">A</span>1500mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">B1</span>2mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">B2</span>2mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">B6</span>2.25mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">B12</span>4.5mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">BT</span>3450mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">C</span>187.5mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">D</span>10mg、V<span style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom;\">E</span>22.5mg、</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">泛酸8.5mg、烟酸19mg、叶酸 775mg、胆碱975mg、生物素64mg</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">热量：1175KJ</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉完全符合合理膳食的要求，做到了高蛋白、低脂肪、高膳食纤维，维生素和矿物质种类充足搭配合理，</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">并提供人体所需的热量。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff3300;\">均衡营养，享&ldquo;瘦&rdquo;生活每一天</span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 减肥是现在大多数人聊天的共同话题，胖人必须减，标准体重的人也要减。节食、运动、拉肚子是减肥的三部曲，痛苦、反弹、</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">没效果是减肥的主旋律。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>减！减！减！减坏了身体，</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>减坏了胃，减出了内分泌失调、厌食症！</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>这样是瘦身还是受罪？</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉，一种通过均衡体内营养物质，控制糖类、脂肪的摄入量，增加饱腹感，减少高油高脂等垃圾食品的食</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">用量的健康自然减肥方法应运而生。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 服用瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉，您不需要主动节食，因为没有饥饿感，你就可以暂时忘记美食的诱惑。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 服用瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉，不必担心因营养摄入不足而造成内分泌失调，或得上恐怖的厌食症。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 服用瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉，不需要每天想着去8趟厕所，因为丰富的纤维素会滋润你的肠道，轻轻松松排出油脂便。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 服用瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉，真的能减肥吗？看看它的成分就知道了</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 瑞倪维儿蛋白魔纤冲调粉主要成分&mdash;&mdash;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>左旋肉碱：</strong>俗称脂肪燃烧弹，是一种从瘦肉中提取的，能促使脂肪转化为能量的类氨基酸。配合有氧运动，能</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">起到燃烧脂肪，减轻体重的作用。同时还能保护心脏，降低胆固醇和甘油三酯在血液中的水平。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>魔芋：</strong>是目前发现的唯一能大量提供葡甘露聚糖的作物，它不仅含有人体所需的10多种氨基酸，还含有多种微量元素和矿物质。低</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">脂肪、高纤维、膨胀率高是魔芋的特性。因此魔芋具有降血脂、降血糖、降血压、减肥、润肠、补钙、美容、保健等多种功效。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>脱脂大豆蛋白+乳清蛋白：</strong>双蛋白，同时补充动物蛋白和植物蛋白，满足人体日常所须营养物质，让每个细胞摆脱&ldquo;饥饿&rdquo;，彻底</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">告别节食减肥的痛苦和副作用。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>骨胶原粉：</strong>能延长脂肪燃烧的时间，睡眠时作用效果更加显著。还能补充人体必须的钙质和胶原蛋白，令骨骼坚韧，皮肤细腻、柔</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">滑、富有弹性。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd1.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/119198006/T2u_rEXstaXXXXXXXX_!!119198006.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absmiddle\" /></p>','2607','保健品	保健食品	冲剂','康婷生物','0','','','1','0',null,'1402776240','1403552136','274','data/files/store_358/goods_12/small_201406151156529460.jpg','1','2595','2596','2607','0','299.00','120','');
